        <h1 class="acl-title">China — AI Copyright Law</h1>
        <p class="acl-excerpt">China has taken a rapid, pragmatic approach to AI regulation, notably becoming the first major jurisdiction to recognize copyright protection for certain AI-generated images based on human prompt engineering.</p>
      </div>
